{"tid":2069471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」銅鑼灣驚現大型墓碑","createTime":"2020-06-18T11:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T04:00:06.000Z","uid":114360,"like":508,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"febefb67436a604b771adf70a9ee5a01082f6a51","tid":2069471,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76kE9kZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76kE9kZ.jpg&h=4cd04c70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母 嚇死人"},{"pid":"f06ec8e9df63bf499c835e70e01f6ab1cec9bb1f","tid":2069471,"uid":114360,"like":245,"dislike":1,"score":244,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"大家快D跟民間清算師一起去投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTO: tellme@1823.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n本人透過傳媒及社交平台得知銅鑼灣怡和街香港大廈近日有兩個新建大型戶外招牌，圖中所見現正張貼一名中年男子張國鈞先生的寫真集，相信新招牌連同現有已建成招牌及平台屋均為違法僭建物並無向政府相關部門入則申請，要求派員實地視察。<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署：<br />\n此乃新建大型戶外招牌，同時有戶外電源接駁，擔心違法建築會為大廈結構，以及途人帶來極大風險。<br />\n<br />\n同時該大廈外圍有多個大型招牌及平台屋，懷疑同樣為僭建物，懷疑日久失修以及在新建招牌影響風壓下，擔心會出現擾流效應，要求風季前即時處理。<br />\n<br />\n差餉物業估價署：<br />\n此大廈外圍有多個大型戶外招牌以及平台僭建屋，相信有關人士／法團未有向差餉物業估價署申報，要求跟進。<br />\n<br />\n 此致<br />\n各相關部門"},{"pid":"7794dd31c866ee0c9f260df740756ac27efee5f6","tid":2069471,"uid":192409,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣紅磡嗰邊都有啦 琼子同鄭泳舜"},{"pid":"f18bbb314c7428d874375b12ba6d49ffc497f52b","tid":2069471,"uid":8307,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"上面好dom本下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"